name: cpf
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool quadro_de_s_cios_cpf_cnpj.
Tool description: Consultar Quadro de Sócios e Administradores registrados na Receita Federal
API description: Fetches information of a partner or administrator based on their CPF (Cadastro de Pessoas Físicas).

cpf.description: The CPF number of the partner or administrator.

nome.description: The name of the partner or administrator. Providing the name can improve the chances of finding the data.
